      "screen_name": "aakashgupta",
      "created_at": "Fri Apr 03 09:04:02 +0000 2026",
      "full_text": "The real story here is who made these nuggets.\n\nDorada Foods is a joint venture between Lopez Foods and Tyson, originally built in Ponca City, Oklahoma to be McDonald's third chicken nugget supplier. They make McNuggets, McChicken, and Spicy McChicken patties for the golden",
